    public class SpatialClassDescriptor
extends it.emarolab.owloop.aMORDescriptor.utility.MORConceptBase
implements it.emarolab.owloop.aMORDescriptor.MORConcept.Sub<SpatialClassDescriptor>, it.emarolab.owloop.aMORDescriptor.MORConcept.Classify<SpatialIndividualDescriptor>
    The OWLOOP Descriptor for a class representing a abstract Object.

    This is an OWLClass Descriptor based on the OWLOOP API. It is in charge to synchronise the individuals classified in this class, as well as sub classes.
